2. cs.GR (Graphics) is also likely as the paper involves the generation of animated characters. 
3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper uses a deep neural network for facial expression recognition. 
4. cs.LG (Machine Learning) is a possible category as the paper involves the training of a GAN for many-to-one identity mapping. 
5. cs.MM (Multimedia) is a less likely category but still possible as the paper deals with the generation of animated characters and facial expression recognition.
